00:03:48.560 --> 00:03:54.320
[Amit Varma]: people they're supposed to help? Why was demonetization a bad idea? How should GST have

00:03:54.320 --> 00:04:00.080
[Amit Varma]: been implemented? Why are all our politicians so corrupt when not all of them are bad people?

