00:18:01.600 --> 00:18:06.960
[Guest]: take it for granted, right? You see a woman or a woman sees you, you're seen to each other. Yeah,

00:18:06.960 --> 00:18:14.240
[Guest]: there's nothing like the unseen. But here you have to present yourselves. And that's when you know,

00:18:14.240 --> 00:18:19.200
[Guest]: from all your choices, the way you dress, to the way you talk, to the way you walk, to what you're

00:18:19.200 --> 00:18:25.120
[Guest]: reading, to what interests you have to all of that, you want some way of signaling that you're

00:18:25.120 --> 00:18:32.080
