00:23:30.400 --> 00:23:37.760
[Guest]: right? That, that how it's either going to be this or that, or something else. So I think it's so

00:23:37.760 --> 00:23:42.000
[Guest]: clear the communication is transparently transactional. So there's nothing else.

00:23:42.000 --> 00:23:47.440
[Guest]: Yeah. Like you move with the idea, like if somebody says he's, he's a little discreet or

00:23:48.160 --> 00:23:54.000
[Guest]: closeted or whatever, you know, he's not going to give you his number, you have to still go by

00:23:54.000 --> 00:23:58.720
[Guest]: the trust factor and meet him where he wants you to meet him, if you're interested,

00:23:58.720 --> 00:24:04.480
[Guest]: if there's been a conversation, if there's some chemistry. So you have to take that risk. Like

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:08.720
[Guest]: earlier, though, I wouldn't be able to see a picture of somebody online because people wouldn't,

00:24:08.720 --> 00:24:13.840
[Guest]: there's to be no option of sharing pictures. You just met. And then you took it from there.

00:24:13.840 --> 00:24:15.760
[Amit Varma]: And so you didn't even know who you were meeting.

00:24:15.760 --> 00:24:19.360
[Amit Varma]: You have an account of a date you had at just around the corner, which, which again,

00:24:19.360 --> 00:24:23.840
[Amit Varma]: makes me very nostalgic, because just around the corner is like a defines a certain time in Bombay

00:24:23.840 --> 00:24:28.960
[Amit Varma]: and a certain time in Bandra. And he had portrayed himself as I think being very tall, and he turned

00:24:28.960 --> 00:24:34.080
[Guest]: out to be really short, very short. Yeah. And you still went along.

00:24:34.080 --> 00:24:39.520
[Guest]: I was, I was in a sense desperate. I was young. I was horny. I was desperate.

00:24:40.320 --> 00:24:43.280
[Guest]: And, and I just wanted to experience everything.

00:24:43.920 --> 00:24:47.360
[Amit Varma]: You also got a very interesting account of how you seduced a straight man.

00:24:47.360 --> 00:24:48.720
[Amit Varma]: Yeah, at Cafe Mondega.

00:24:48.720 --> 00:24:49.440
[Amit Varma]: So what happened there?

00:24:50.000 --> 00:24:56.080
