00:29:09.280 --> 00:29:10.320
[Guest]: Once I was out of there.

00:29:10.880 --> 00:29:13.680
[Amit Varma]: And how was college? Where did you go to college?

00:29:13.680 --> 00:29:14.880
[Guest]: Right here in Bombay.

00:29:14.880 --> 00:29:16.720
[Guest]: Okay. How was college?

00:29:16.720 --> 00:29:22.240
