00:29:22.960 --> 00:29:27.200
[Guest]: I was immersed in books. My professors were very, very kind.

00:29:27.920 --> 00:29:31.680
[Guest]: And I went to St. Xavier's. So yeah, so it was a lot of fun.

00:29:31.680 --> 00:29:36.640
[Guest]: It was something that was so different. It was, yeah, but again, in college, right?

00:29:36.640 --> 00:29:39.920
